      Customer constructor Used by DBCustomer.getAllCustomers()
      Parameters:
      customerID - customerID is primary key
      customerName - name of customer
      customerAddress - address of customer
      divisionName - name of first level division associated with divisionID
      divisionID - id of state or province (first level division) associated with customer, divisionID is foreign key
      countryName - name of country associated with divisionID associated with customer
      postal - postal code of customer
      phone - phone number of customer
